<item>
            <title>[PIG-1302] Include zebra&apos;s &quot;pigtest&quot; ant target as a part of pig&apos;s ant test target</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1302</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are changes made in Pig interfaces which break zebra loaders/storers. It would be good to run the pig tests in the zebra unit tests as part of running pig&apos;s core-test for each patch submission. So essentially in the &quot;test&quot; ant target in pig, we would need to invoke zebra&apos;s &quot;pigtest&quot; target.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12459316">PIG-1302</key>
            <summary>Include zebra&apos;s &quot;pigtest&quot; ant target as a part of pig&apos;s ant test target</summary>
                <type id="4" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/issuetypes/improvement.png">Improvement</type>
                                            <priority id="3" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/priorities/major.png">Major</priority>
                        <status id="6" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/statuses/closed.png" description="The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.">Closed</status>
                    <statusCategory id="3" key="done" colorName="green"/>
                                    <resolution id="1">Fixed</resolution>
                                        <assignee username="gkesavan">Giridharan Kesavan</assignee>
